r i dont have and will get my unbuffed mr to 150ish..120 in ac gear.  the rbb combo will give me 195 hps where the cocw will give mejust the base 70 which makes the rbb combo look better.  also my buffed str is only 230ish so the str would basically max me.  Im not sure how much of a difference the 31% haste will be as compared to the 36% with a 44 44 weapon cause ill always be with an epic chanter.  I also like the cloak of incons cause its a bit better than cloak of fearsome and ill probably get a belt of the destryer soon~<br><br>aspit<br>60 human warlord tz <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/udumeshuhlbelk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dumesh UhlBelk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/19/02 1:33:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1684.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://personal.bhm.bellsouth.net/bhm/w/i/wilsonua/DumStare.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: cocw + belt of inconsistance vs cloak of confusion + rbb</span><hr size=1> Given that your next most likely haste upgrade is the belt, that you are already at 1250AC, that your stamina needs work, and that you always have access to shissar; I would go with the RBB combo. <p><a href="http://www.gaijindesign.com/lawriemalen/jedi" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.gaijindesign.com/lawriemalen/jedi/jedimaster.jpg" width="285" height="123" border="0"><br></a><a href = "http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=5309"target="_blank"alt = "Korak's Megalo Profile"><FONT SIZE="2"><b>Korak Sarathai - 59 Barbarian Myrmidon - The Hand</b></FONT><BR></a></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><t